 Why Use Promises?

✔ Avoid callback hell

✔ Better readability

✔ Easier error handling

✔ Cleaner async code



 When to Use Promises

API calls 

Database operations 

File handling 

Timers 



 Conclusion

Promises simplify asynchronous programming in JavaScript

They replace messy callbacks with clean, readable code
